channel.title: SourceForge.net: Project File Releases: Pulse Programmer
channel.description: SF.net File Releases: Pulse Programmer (pulse-sequencer project) - A programmable signal generator and RF synthesizer for scientific experiments, especially quantum computing and quantum information processing. It includes hardware, firmware, software, and documentation, all under an open source license.
